metadata.name: Sacrificing Satoshi
metadata.description:
A scene of the sacrifice of Satoshi Nakamoto's persona by the individual or group responsible for the Bitcoin project. Inariâ€™s Satoshi outfit is a combination of all the clues, suspects, and known facts about Satoshi Nakamoto, including the entirety of the Bitcoin whitepaper. Satoshi Nakamoto was a persona that served its purpose and was sacrificed by its creator for the benefit and security of Bitcoin and its creators.
